reviewText: Loved the flow of the relaxing stretching movement with the classical music.  A good morning stretch,but would like more variety in the different workouts,
This dvd came promptly and was what I had wanted.
One of the DVDs is hard to see because it's dark. The other is fine
I enjoyed the music and the stretching exercise.

I have been using this video every morning for 5 months now (I first used the free version on amazon prime, until this updated DVD came out).  I definitely have more flexibility and less muscle soreness after working out.  The stretching gets me ready physically for my day.  It wasn't that easy at first, but I stuck with it, and now I can do the entire routine myself without prompting.
